### ============================================
### 变量
### ============================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@aiUrl = http://localhost:5001
@nginxUrl = http://39.106.209.208:9092
@internalToken = smart-class-ai-internal-token-2026
@jwt = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### ============================================
### 0. 健康检查 & 登录
### ============================================

### 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/health

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"admin","password":"admin123"}

### 注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"newuser","password":"123456","nickname":"新用户"}

### 注册-用户名重复
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"admin","password":"123456"}

### 注册-参数校验（用户名过短）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"a","password":"123456"}

### 注册-参数校验（密码过短）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"testuser","password":"123"}

### 获取当前用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/info
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### ============================================
### 0.1 用户管理（admin 专用）
### ============================================

### 用户列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 用户列表-按角色筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?role=teacher&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 用户列表-按状态筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?status=enabled&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 用户详情（需替换真实 id）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 编辑用户（昵称/头像）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"nickname":"张老师","avatarUrl":""}

### 变更用户角色（admin→teacher 或 teacher→admin）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2/role
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"role":"teacher"}

### 禁用用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2/status
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status":"disabled"}

### 启用用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2/status
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status":"enabled"}

### 删除用户（软删除）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### ============================================
### 0.2 RBAC 权限验证
### ============================================

### teacher 登录（用于权限对比测试）
# @name teacherLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"teacher","password":"teacher123"}

### teacher 读视频源（应 200）
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### teacher 新增视频源（应 403）
POST {{baseUrl}}/streams
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherLogin.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"stream_name":"test","stream_id":"test_01","rtmp_url":"rtmp://localhost:9090/live/test_01","remark":""}

### teacher 新增人员（应 403）
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherLogin.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"student_no":"9999","name":"test","class_name":"test"}

### teacher 查操作日志（应 403）
GET {{baseUrl}}/operation-logs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### teacher 访问用户管理（应 403）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### admin 新增视频源（应 200）
POST {{baseUrl}}/streams
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"stream_name":"test","stream_id":"test_01","rtmp_url":"rtmp://localhost:9090/live/test_01","remark":""}

### admin 访问用户管理（应 200）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### ============================================
### 一、AI → Spring Boot（带 X-Internal-Token）
### ============================================

### 1.1 视频流列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

### 1.2 区域列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/zones?stream_id=classroom_01
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

### 1.3 规则列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/rules
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

### 1.4 人脸特征
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/face-features
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}

### 1.5 告警入库
POST {{baseUrl}}/alerts/ai
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "evt_20260710143000001",
  "stream_id": "classroom_01",
  "alert_type": "danger_zone_intrusion",
  "alert_name": "危险区域入侵",
  "level": "warning",
  "confidence": 0.85,
  "occurred_at": "2026-07-10T14:30:00+08:00",
  "duration_seconds": 3.5,
  "student_id": null,
  "target_info": {"track_id":1,"bbox":[100,200,150,300]},
  "zone_id": 1,
  "snapshot_path": "/snapshots/evt_xxx.jpg",
  "record_path": null,
  "event_time_offset": null,
  "extra": {"source":"backend_ai"}
}

### ============================================
### 二、前端 → Spring Boot（带 JWT）
### ============================================

### --- 视频源 ---

### 视频源列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 已启用视频源
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/enabled
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 新增视频源
POST {{baseUrl}}/streams
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"stream_name":"3号教室","stream_id":"classroom_03","rtmp_url":"rtmp://localhost:9090/live/classroom_03","remark":""}

### 推流状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/classroom_01/status
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 播放地址
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/classroom_01/preview-url
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### --- 区域 ---

### 区域列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/zones?streamId=classroom_01&zoneType=danger
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 新增区域
POST {{baseUrl}}/zones
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"stream_id":"classroom_01","zone_name":"讲台危险区","zone_type":"danger","coordinates":"[{\"x\":0.1,\"y\":0.1},{\"x\":0.5,\"y\":0.1},{\"x\":0.5,\"y\":0.5},{\"x\":0.1,\"y\":0.5}]","threshold_seconds":2,"safe_distance":0.05}

### 某视频源全部区域
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/classroom_01/zones
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### --- 规则 ---

### 规则列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 新增规则
POST {{baseUrl}}/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"rule_type":"danger_zone","rule_name":"危险区域检测","enabled":true,"threshold_seconds":2,"confidence_threshold":0.6,"cooldown_seconds":45,"level":"warning","config_json":"{\"safe_distance\":0.05}"}

### --- 人员 ---

### 人员列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 新增人员
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"student_no":"2024001","name":"张三","class_name":"软件工程1班"}

### 人脸注册（需替换真实 base64 图片，会调 AI）
POST {{baseUrl}}/students/1/face
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"image":""}

### --- 告警 ---

### 告警列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 告警统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/alert-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 更新告警状态（需替换真实 id）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/alerts/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"status":"processing","handler_id":1,"remark":"正在处理"}

### --- 录像 & 日志 ---

### 录像列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/recordings?streamId=classroom_01&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 操作日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/operation-logs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### ============================================
### 三、AI 补充接口
### ============================================

### 分析摘要
GET {{aiUrl}}/analysis/summary/classroom_01

### 触发 AI 重载配置
POST {{aiUrl}}/config/reload

### 重载人脸特征
POST {{aiUrl}}/face/features/reload

### ============================================
### 四、截图 & 证据（AI → 云服务器 Nginx）
### ============================================

### AI 本地截图（Flask fallback，开发环境用）
GET {{aiUrl}}/snapshots/20260712/evt_test.jpg

### 云服务器 Nginx 截图（生产环境，前端实际访问路径）
GET {{nginxUrl}}/snapshots/20260712/evt_b10caf1f1fe840f3.jpg

### AI 模型状态（含 snapshot_pusher 是否启用）
GET {{aiUrl}}/model/status